'ello,

   Well, after weeks of additions, revisions and general fussing... ;-) here
is the first "official" release of the New Order Discography by Dennis and
myself.  I think we are both amazed/impressed by what we have, and hope that
other NO fans, and the Inet community in general, will find this of value.

   If anyone has anything to add to this, or correct, please feel free to
send email.  I know of a least 1 item that exists (a Canadian CD5 for
"Round & Round" in a cardboard sleeve, saw it in Toronto, but have all
mixes already) that is not in the discography.

   We are also working on discographies for Electronic, Revenge and The Other
Two (the latter won't be out for awhile for obvious reasons ;-), and hope to
have the first two available soon.  Entries for these are also appreciated.

   And now without further ado, I give you the "New Order Discography"...
just remember to ignore my .sig... ;-)

-Rich

